0.title: Frontend Developer needed for React & TypeScript web application
0.description:
We are looking for an experienced Frontend Developer to join our team for a web application development project.

**What you'll be working on:**
- Building responsive, modern web applications using React and TypeScript
- Implementing clean, maintainable, and scalable code
- Creating reusable UI components and integrating with APIs
- Ensuring cross-browser compatibility and optimal performance
- Collaborating closely with our design and backend teams

**Required Skills & Experience:**
- Strong proficiency in React (minimum 2+ years)
- Solid experience with TypeScript for type-safe development
- Expert knowledge of JavaScript, HTML5, and CSS3
- Experience with modern frontend tooling and build processes
- Understanding of responsive design principles
- Knowledge of version control (Git)

**Project Details:**
- Duration: 1-3 months
- Medium-sized, well-defined project scope
- Hourly rate: $30-55/hour based on experience
- Remote work opportunity

**Communication & Work Style:**
- Regular updates and progress reports
- Collaborative approach with team meetings
- Proactive communication about challenges or blockers
- Adherence to coding standards and best practices

If you're passionate about creating exceptional user experiences and have the technical expertise we're looking for, we'd love to hear from you!
